text: Heteroclytomorpha quadrinotata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Blanchard in 1853. It is known from the Solomon Islands.BioLib.cz - Heteroclytomorpha quadrinotata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Homonoeini Category:Beetles described in 1853
